we just want you to sing a little song...

35:34.448 --> 35:36.143
...make the people feel good.

35:36.350 --> 35:39.080
What do you already know?
You know what she's gonna sing.

35:39.287 --> 35:41.482
Hold this, Freddie.
Don't steal nothing.

35:41.689 --> 35:44.681
Miss Wilma. Let's do it.

35:44.892 --> 35:47.383
