to all you beautiful faces...

35:47.595 --> 35:51.759
...but especially to April.

39:01.856 --> 39:03.619
Thank you.

39:06.193 --> 39:09.424
Y'all go straight in the house,
you understand?

39:11.832 --> 39:14.266
Boy, don't be slamming my door.

39:15.069 --> 39:16.866
Hey, wait.

39:22.309 --> 39:23.833
Thank you. Hey, how was it?

39:24.045 --> 39:28.209
I don't wanna steal nothing else
if that's what I gotta do to pay it back.

39:28.416 --> 39:29.713
That lady's crazy.

39:32.553 --> 39:36.148
That means all of your decisions,
your choices...

39:36.357 --> 39:37.790
...they all have a price to pay.

39:37.992 --> 39:40.756
So you do the crime,
you gotta do the time.

39:40.961 --> 39:42.451
Yeah, whatever.

39:42.663 --> 39:44.961
Look, we ought to take a bath.
Go on upstairs.

39:45.166 --> 39:46.861
Jennifer.

39:48.035 --> 39:49.525
What's this?

39:52.573 --> 39:54.040
You bought his insulin.

39:56.477 --> 39:57.774
I was gonna do it.

39:58.379 --> 40:00.370
Well, now you don't have to.

40:03.684 --> 40:05.709
Why are you so nice to us?

40:05.920 --> 40:08.889
-I don't understand that question.
-You nice, why?

40:09.090 --> 40:10.580
Why not?

40:10.791 --> 40:13.089
You should expect people
to be nice to you.

40:13.294 --> 40:15.125
You shouldn't expect people
to be mean.

40:15.329 --> 40:16.591
Not in this world.

40:16.797 --> 40:19.789
-You get what you expect, right?
-I guess.

40:22.736 --> 40:24.465
You do a great job
with your brothers.

40:26.474 --> 40:28.567
I'm all they got.

40:51.799 --> 40:54.165
Oh, come on.
What the hell is Mexico up to?

40:54.368 --> 40:55.665
Are you serious?

41:01.175 --> 41:02.164
Hey.

41:02.376 --> 41:04.276
What--?
Do you know what time it is?

41:05.279 --> 41:08.908
-Yeah, it's 1 :30 in the afternoon.
-What are you doing?

41:09.116 --> 41:11.277
-I'm working off my debt.
-What?

41:12.086 --> 41:14.646
I figured that I'd get up this morning,
get to work.

41:14.855 --> 41:17.881
Figured if I fixed this floor,
then the kids can stay in this room.

41:18.092 --> 41:19.923
You don't have to worry
about those kids.

41:20.127 --> 41:23.824
They're not staying, pack up your tools
and go back down in the basement.

41:24.498 --> 41:26.159
Why not?
Why they don't stay in here?

41:27.067 --> 41:30.230
What do you mean--?
Hey, hey, hey!

41:30.437 --> 41:32.962
Hey!

41:33.174 --> 41:35.438
Stop it! Stop it!

41:36.043 --> 41:39.137
Look, you have a serious problem
with this floor, okay?

41:39.346 --> 41:40.335
I know that.

41:40.548 --> 41:42.448
That's why no one
ever comes up here...

41:42.650 --> 41:46.142
...and that's why I keep
the door closed. For safety, okay?

41:46.353 --> 41:48.617
These kids,
they need a room of their own.

41:48.822 --> 41:51.882
Why are you so worried about kids
that don't even belong to you?

41:52.092 --> 41:53.525
-What's up?
-That's your family.

41:53.727 --> 41:54.887
Why you not concerned?

41:55.429 --> 41:58.193
Jennifer has nightmares every night.
Manny, night sweats.

41:58.399 --> 42:01.459
Byron, he tosses and turns
in his sleep.

42:01.669 --> 42:03.899
Can you imagine
what those kids have been through?

42:04.104 --> 42:05.696
I just wanna help them.

42:06.540 --> 42:08.701
You wanna help them?

42:08.909 --> 42:11.377
You live in my basement.
You can't even help yourself.

42:11.579 --> 42:12.637
How are you gonna help?

42:12.846 --> 42:16.213
-By giving them this room.
-No, no, you're not.

42:16.417 --> 42:17.611
This is my house.

42:19.887 --> 42:22.822
You can't give them nothing
that doesn't belong to you.

42:23.023 --> 42:26.220
If you're so worried about the kids,
why are you making so much noise?

42:26.427 --> 42:29.260
-You're waking them up.
-They were gone before I got up.

42:29.463 --> 42:32.159
Well, where did they go?
Since you know so much about them.

42:32.366 --> 42:33.355
I don't know.

42:33.567 --> 42:36.661
What do you care? You don't even
make them comfortable to stay here.

42:36.870 --> 42:39.566
That's right, three less things
I gotta worry about.

42:39.773 --> 42:43.231
Pack up your little tools and follow me
back down to the basement, come on.

42:43.444 --> 42:44.911
-You know, you don't--
-Let's go.

42:45.112 --> 42:46.272
You don't even mean that.

42:46.747 --> 42:48.112
You don't know me.

42:48.315 --> 42:50.215
-Let's go, back to your blind spot.
-Hey.

42:50.417 --> 42:52.442
These kids need someone.
They need some help.

42:52.653 --> 42:54.712
Okay, well,
when my mama comes back...

42:54.922 --> 42:58.517
...she will come and get them,
and they will have someone, happy?

42:59.426 --> 43:01.894
You're not this heartless, April.

43:02.096 --> 43:03.688
So why do you do this?

43:03.897 --> 43:05.922
Is it because of your man?

43:06.133 --> 43:07.862
Is it because of him?

43:09.703 --> 43:11.261
You know, you're too good for him.

43:13.407 --> 43:15.932
