43:18.312 --> 43:21.873
Okay, I'll finish up
after your man wakes up.

43:22.349 --> 43:23.976
Thank you.

43:32.293 --> 43:35.126
I'm coming. Shoot.

43:46.940 --> 43:48.168
Pastor.

43:49.109 --> 43:52.306
Miss Wilma.
What are you guys doing here?

43:52.513 --> 43:54.913
