-Yeah, as much as she'll let me.

44:09.563 --> 44:12.396
Great job in the chapel.
We even have a check for you.

44:12.599 --> 44:15.534
Well, that's great.
I'll come by to pick it up.

44:15.736 --> 44:17.363
Hello?

44:17.705 --> 44:20.640
