Because I can go back to bed.

44:20.841 --> 44:22.706
April, can we sit down?

44:22.910 --> 44:24.878
Yeah, sure.

44:44.131 --> 44:45.496
What is it?

44:46.600 --> 44:49.160
It's about your mother.

44:49.670 --> 44:52.833
