44:56.310 --> 44:57.800
What?

44:59.913 --> 45:01.847
What?

45:02.816 --> 45:04.044
I'm sorry, baby.

45:04.251 --> 45:07.414
-When?
-About a week ago.

45:14.228 --> 45:17.686
-What happened?
