45:34.014 --> 45:35.242
She....

45:35.449 --> 45:38.213
They assumed she was just asleep.

45:39.086 --> 45:43.785
And when the driver tried to wake her,
it was too late.

45:44.324 --> 45:46.884
There was nothing anyone could do.

45:47.094 --> 45:48.891
I'm sorry.

45:50.364 --> 45:52.889
She was at the city morgue.

45:53.100 --> 45:55.034
No one claimed her.

45:55.636 --> 45:57.968
No identification.

46:01.809 --> 46:04.403
