and get them.

46:32.105 --> 46:34.096
I'm sorry, April.

46:41.014 --> 46:46.281
If you need anything, April,
just come by the church.

46:47.955 --> 46:49.183
You take care of her, huh?

46:49.723 --> 46:51.623
