56:10.784 --> 56:12.217
I gotta go to Calvary. I'm late."

56:12.419 --> 56:15.445
Jesus went to the cross. He said,
"I'm gonna send you a comforter.

56:15.655 --> 56:17.885
When the comforter come,
you gonna be all right."

56:18.091 --> 56:19.718
So he's swimming.
He try and swim.

56:19.926 --> 56:21.894
He's worried, Jaws was coming,
all that--

56:22.095 --> 56:23.687
Spielberg had did that Jaws thing.

56:23.897 --> 56:25.626
It was surrounding him.
He was worried.

56:25.832 --> 56:27.663
-You know what happened?
-What?

56:27.867 --> 56:29.027
Just in the nick of time--

56:29.235 --> 56:31.066
When you think
you ain't gonna make it...

56:31.271 --> 56:33.136
...in the nick of time,
something happens.

56:33.339 --> 56:34.829
Noah came up in the arch.

56:35.742 --> 56:39.234
That's right, Noah came rowing up
in the arch of St. Louis Arch...

56:39.446 --> 56:41.437
